From 40dcc6589f187b031bd5856ac6627dc8a4b91902 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Allen Ye <allen.ye@mediatek.com>
Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 00:54:49 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 58/89] mtk: mt76: mt7996: Add lpi support with sku_idx and
 enhancement

Add lpi support with sku_idx and enhancement.
1. Add sku index for lpi sku table
2. Add lpi psd limit for psd country and compensate power by fw.
3. Add lpi mode mamangement from enhancement that use 1T to transmit mgmt
from in 80 MHz.

Signed-off-by: Allen Ye <allen.ye@mediatek.com>

Fix wrong maximum power by checkinh max_power of operating channel.

Signed-off-by: Allen Ye <allen.ye@mediatek.com>
